item.title: The Dig - E03 - Double episode: Death of a team member, part 1 of 2
item.description:
The Dig - E03 - Double episode: Death of a team member, part 1 of 2

A deep space adventure by Sean Clark in collaboration with filmmaker Steven Spielberg. A radio telescope in Borneo detects the approach of a large asteroid on a collision course with Earth; authorities dub it "Attila" after the ancient conqueror Attila the Hun.
